==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Palatable
<hw>Pal"a*ta*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Palate</er>.]</ety> <def>Agreeable to the palate or taste; savory;
hence, acceptable; pleasing; <as>as, <ex>palatable</ex> food;
<ex>palatable</ex> advice. Opposite of
<ant>unpalatable</ant>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palatableness</ent>⟦br⟧
